author: National Geographic
description:
Narrated by acclaimed actress Blake Lively, National Geographic invites you into the breathtaking world of emperor penguins. Witness their beautiful mating journey, from courtship rituals to the critical moment of the egg handover. Observe emperor penguins as they meticulously 'practice' the delicate exchange of the egg in never-before-seen footage: an intimate glimpse into their remarkable dedication as parents.

Secrets of the Penguins is now streaming on @disneyplus and @hulu. https://on.natgeo.com/4cHzyFv
